# ManeLine / OAG engagement repo — .gitignore
# --------------------------------------------------------------
# What this file does:
#   Tells Git which files to ignore so we never accidentally
#   commit secrets, credentials, or tool-generated noise.
#   Lines starting with # are comments.
# --------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Secrets & credentials (NEVER commit) ---
# Plain-text credential files. Recreate locally as needed.
Silver Lining Logins.txt
*Logins.txt
*.secrets
.env
.env.*
env.local.txt
env.*.txt

# --- Cloudflare Wrangler tool cache ---
# Auto-generated by `npx wrangler` — safe to delete anytime,
# Wrangler will rebuild it.
.wrangler/

# --- Supabase CLI local state ---
# Contains a link to the remote project (not secret, but
# machine-specific — regenerated by `supabase link`).
supabase/.temp/
supabase/.branches/

# --- Node / npm (in case you ever add a package.json) ---
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# --- Claude Code local state ---
.claude/

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~
